== 製作 ==
《活屍大軍：拉斯維加斯的陷落》為2021年[[Netflix|Netflix]]電影《[[活屍大軍|活屍大軍]]》的衍生作品，由位於加拿大[[蒙特婁|蒙特婁]]的梅杜扎特動畫（{{lang|en|Meduzarts Animation}}）負責主要動畫製作，主要講述史考特·沃德（{{lang|en|Scott Ward}}，[[戴夫·巴帝斯塔|戴夫·巴帝斯塔]]配音）和他的搶劫團隊在[[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]]最初淪陷期間的起源故事，同時揭露喪屍爆發的神秘源頭。2020年9月，[[Netflix|Netflix]]批准該動畫和前傳電影《[[活屍大軍前傳|活屍大軍前傳]]》的製作，電影部份演員回歸配音他們各自的角色，查克·史奈德和{{le|傑·奧利瓦|Jay Oliva}}確認將執導其中的兩集。<ref name="Deadline(2020-09-03)">{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2020/09/zack-snyder-netflix-army-of-the-dead-movie-prequel-anime-series-1234569725/|title=Zack Snyder Netflix Zombie Pic ‘Army Of The Dead’ Spawning Film Prequel & Anime Series|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2020-09-03|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904131630/https://deadline.com/2020/09/zack-snyder-netflix-army-of-the-dead-movie-prequel-anime-series-1234569725/|archive-date=2020-09-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>10月初，[[喬·曼格尼洛|喬·曼格尼洛]]、[[克利斯汀·史萊特|克利斯汀·史萊特]]、[[亨利·藍尼克斯|亨利·藍尼克斯]]和[[凡妮莎·哈金斯|凡妮莎·哈金斯]]等演員加入配音陣容<ref name="AnimationMagazine(2020-10-01)" /><ref name="ScreenRant(2020-10-01)">{{cite news|url=https://screenrant.com/army-dead-lost-vegas-zack-snyder-netflix-cast/|title=Netflix’s Army Of The Dead: Lost Vegas Sets Full Cast Including Joe Manganiello|last=Hussaini|first=Syed Fahadullah|work=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]]|date=2020-10-01|accessdate=2020-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019085313/https://screenrant.com/army-dead-lost-vegas-zack-snyder-netflix-cast/|archive-date=2020-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="FlickeringMyth(2020-10-05)">{{cite news|url=https://www.flickeringmyth.com/2020/10/zack-snyder-army-of-the-dead-lost-vegas-anime-cast-announced-with-joe-manganiello-christian-slater-vanessa-hudgens-and-more/|title=Zack Snyder’s Army of the Dead: Lost Vegas anime cast announced with Joe Manganiello, Christian Slater, Vanessa Hudgens and more|last=Church|first=Ricky|work=Flickering Myth|date=2020-10-05|accessdate=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216